OL,5, British teenager Alex Batty has        
OL,6, revealed he lied about the details of  
OL,7, his escape to protect his mother and   
OL,8, grandfather from police.               
OL,10,FIn an interview with The Sun, he said  
OL,11,Fhe fabricated a story about a four-day 
OL,12,Fjourney, hoping it would stop officers 
OL,13,Ffrom tracking them down.               
OL,15,FThe teenager was found walking in      
OL,16,FFrance six years after going missing.  
OL,18,FHe said doubts about his mother and    
OL,19,Fgrandfather's nomadic lifestyle began  
OL,20,Fwhen he was "14 or 15 years old".      
